{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"03e635d846","title":"印发少数营团干部对经济生活紧张有抵触情绪的材料的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3631528b0b","index":0,"year":1959,"month":7,"day":5,"articleId":"03e635d846"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"e2e4435517","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"03e635d846","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"尚昆，即杨尚昆，当时任中共中央书记处候补书记、中央办公厅主任。"},{"id":"0a175210bd","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"03e635d846","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中国人民解放军总政治部秘书处1959年6月24日编印的《政治工作简报》第一二四号上转载的这篇材料说，据四十二军政治部和海南军区政治部报告，有少数营团干部对经济生活紧张表示抵触和不满，认为经济生活紧张是全面的，长期不能解决的，否定成立人民公社的必然性和优越性，攻击地方干部，对党在经济生活方面的各项规定也有不满，认为经济紧张是由于路线上有错误。在少数连排干部中，也有类似情况。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e0b33f758c","type":"title","text":"印印发少数营团干部对经济生活紧张有抵触情绪的材料的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"03e635d846"},{"id":"e2e4435517","type":"paragraph","text":"尚昆同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"03e635d846"},{"id":"0a175210bd","type":"paragraph","text":"此件问请印发各同志","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"03e635d846"},{"id":"f96d053bc9","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"03e635d846"},{"id":"acd432f648","type":"paragraph","text":"七月五日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"03e635d846"}],"page":{"id":"526cfa7650","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"03e635d846","start":176,"end":176}}}},"__N_SSG":true}